    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Hallelujah\r\n\r\n**Define:** You've been hired to remix *Hallelujah* by Rosa Linn for a community music showcase. Your challenge is to combine tracks from this song with sounds from the *Acoustic Arcade* pack to create a new emotional vibe.  To do this, you'll need to think carefully about when and how different sounds play together or one after another since they have different lengths and rhythms!\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Listen to the original song and explore the *Acoustic Arcade* pack. Plan how you want your remix to sound and which tracks fit well together. Listen to the example below for what this could sound like!\r\n\r\n**Try:** Build your remix using the code blocks. Use `play together` and `play sequential` to combine sounds in the same moment. Try different combinations and tweak the timing to get the vibe just right!\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#ebe8f1; border: 0; border-radius: 10px; clear:both; padding: 5px\">\r\n\r\nNeed some help? Try the [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i> Docs](#clickable=documentation-button) in the upper-right corner!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** Listen to your song and iterate until it sounds the way you want it to. In order to complete this level, your remix must include:\r\n\r\n- At least 2 vocal tracks\r\n- At least 4 unique tracks from the *Acoustic Arcade* pack",
